**Overview**

This dashboard displays key statistics and visualizations based on Case logs from the Abnormal Security integration. It includes the top 10 affected employees, a breakdown of events by remediation status, severity, analysis and status, as well as essential details about the Case data and total cases.

[**Integrations Page**](/app/integrations/detail/abnormal_security/overview)
